title: Automatic packaging equipment US-TPS-1532
short_description: This US-TPS-1532 equipment has a Panasonic control panel and helps to make the packaging process complete and seamless. The working speed of this packaging equipment ranges from 5 to 28 pieces per minute. The width of the package is 50-150 mm, and the length is 50-300 mm. The equipment weighing 900 kg has a length of 2900 mm, a width of 2470 mm and a height of 1728 mm.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-TPS-1532 uskuna Panasonic boshqaruv paneliga ega va qadoqlash jarayonini to'liq va uzluksiz amalga oshirishga ko'maklashadi. Bu qadoqlash uskunasining ishlash tezligi daqiqasiga 5 tadan 28 tagacha yetadi. Qadoq kengligi 50-150 mm, uzunligi esa 50-300 mm ni tashkil etadi. Vazni 900 kg ni tashkil qiluvchi uskuna uzunligi 2900 mm, kengligi 2470 mm va balandligi 1728 mm dan iborat.
